headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust Announces First Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Date and Conference Call Information
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) will announce first quarter 2025 earnings in a press release to be issued after market close on Thursday, May 8, 2025. The Company will host a conference call on Thursday, May 8 at 5:00 PM ET.
